                     <interp inst="t18330704-113-person1122" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I am porter at St. Peterhouse College, Cambridge. On the 2nd of June, I received a letter directed to the Honourable Mr. Law - I delivered to Mrs. Benstead, as I received it - it was a o ndon letter, and charged 2s.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18330704-113-person1123">
