            . I received the letter from the last witness, on Sunday, the 2nd of June, I called my son and he took it to Mr. Law.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18330704-113-person1124">
                  PHILIP 
                  BUCK BENSTEAD
               <interp inst="t18330704-113-person1124" type="surname" value="BUCK BENSTEAD"></interp>
